,0.037026],"unified_progress":[0.071288,0.11032,0.1095,0.10404,0.10459,0.096309,0.090149,0.08281,0.072615,0.063238,0.054462,0.040683]},{"section":5,"text":"That usually points towards iron deficiency because iron-deficiency anemia typically presents that way.","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.053702,0.09812,0.11092,0.11284,0.10648,0.095817,0.091058,0.081533,0.071339,0.070493,0.056886,0.050812],"unified_progress":[0.05558,0.078576,0.093462,0.10134,0.10139,0.10221,0.098166,0.090342,0.082395,0.079536,0.065437,0.051571]},{"section":6,"text":"But I need to consider other causes too, like chronic disease anemia, which can sometimes be normocytic, or thalassemia, but microcytic hypochromic is classic for iron deficiency.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.043006,0.085515,0.09997,0.10585,0.10508,0.099283,0.096348,0.088254,0.079103,0.078108,0.063878,0.055598],"unified_progress":[0.041218,0.071845,0.089391,0.098338,0.10222,0.10426,0.10122,0.095705,0.089119,0.084357,0.069192,0.053129]},{"section":7,"text":"Now, the barium swallow showing a \"leather bottle\" appearance of the stomach.","dimension":5,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.049975,0.098045,0.10148,0.10125,0.096575,0.096665,0.091519,0.085365,0.088778,0.071894,0.062818,0.055629],"unified_progress":[0.049751,0.083797,0.096168,0.10709,0.10746,0.10199,0.096706,0.090588,0.089658,0.070601,0.058368,0.047827]},{"section":8,"text":"Hmm, I remember that term.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.3371,0.056246,0.057006,0.064594,0.062839,0.062992,0.059223,0.065601,0.065305,0.059312,0.062448,0.047331],"unified_progress":[0.22451,0.087678,0.071349,0.068878,0.078622,0.074133,0.083352,0.078528,0.07265,0.057642,0.052387,0.050265]},{"section":9,"text":"Leather bottle stomach is a sign of something specific.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.063507,0.13135,0.064611,0.10593,0.10196,0.10024,0.090225,0.082531,0.074809,0.068983,0.061525,0.054334],"unified_progress":[0.069741,0.093009,0.06944,0.10331,0.10293,0.10555,0.09319,0.090759,0.08288,0.075874,0.063707,0.049607]},{"section":10,"text":"Oh right, it's associated with linitis plastica, which is a type of gastric carcinoma.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.050228,0.08372,0.09121,0.099098,0.10351,0.10131,0.098661,0.090039,0.081026,0.079386,0.063467,0.058349],"unified_progress":[0.058554,0.067358,0.087779,0.096933,0.1001,0.10729,0.10034,0.095586,0.088507,0.080422,0.06487,0.052274]},{"section":11,"text":"The stomach walls become thickened and rigid, losing their normal peristalsis, hence the leather bottle appearance on imaging.","dimension":5,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.040612,0.08592,0.095186,0.099987,0.099199,0.099909,0.097174,0.089893,0.09106,0.076481,0.066277,0.058303],"unified_progress":[0.049369,0.077676,0.095184,0.10404,0.10781,0.10364,0.098619,0.092665,0.089579,0.073007,0.059375,0.049038]},{"section":12,"text":"The microscopic findings are diffusely infiltrating malignant cells with many signet ring cells.","dimension":5,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.047317,0.093318,0.097877,0.098779,0.09621,0.095946,0.09263,0.087701,0.087539,0.076224,0.066758,0.059703],"unified_progress":[0.048139,0.082453,0.095035,0.10246,0.10535,0.10231,0.098058,0.091553,0.088173,0.073882,0.061561,0.051032]},{"section":13,"text":"Signet ring cells are characteristic of adenocarcinoma, especially gastric.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.039136,0.07588,0.087935,0.098231,0.10273,0.10148,0.10073,0.092532,0.085059,0.082688,0.068687,0.064914],"unified_progress":[0.042727,0.063695,0.085127,0.09537,0.099445,0.11407,0.10255,0.096678,0.090553,0.083025,0.069322,0.057432]},{"section":14,"text":"In gastric cancer, signet ring cell carcinoma is a subtype where the cells have a mucin-filled cytoplasm that pushes the nucleus to one side, giving it a signet ring appearance.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.040775,0.077174,0.085837,0.094978,0.10041,0.10173,0.101,0.09385,0.087035,0.085107,0.068914,0.063192],"unified_progress":[0.046204,0.066068,0.084503,0.095906,0.10061,0.10686,0.10244,0.098249,0.092491,0.083306,0.068148,0.055218]},{"section":15,"text":"Putting this together: the patient has symptoms of GI bleeding (dark stools) leading to iron deficiency anemia (microcytic, hypochromic), but the key here is the \"leather bottle\" stomach and the signet ring cells.","dimension":4,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.036833,0.070521,0.079732,0.085555,0.089874,0.092648,0.094601,0.093198,0.093578,0.091672,0.088752,0.083037],"unified_progress":[0.044743,0.063109,0.07486,0.083688,0.090843,0.09771,0.095914,0.096438,0.096608,0.092853,0.0879,0.075333]},{"section":16,"text":"So the primary issue is likely a malignancy.","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.039066,0.072818,0.0857,0.090007,0.088115,0.083805,0.085043,0.083908,0.08485,0.091373,0.08663,0.10869],"unified_progress":[0.042116,0.055639,0.065899,0.077134,0.080464,0.085479,0.087666,0.092558,0.095747,0.099742,0.10499,0.11257]},{"section":17,"text":"The combination of the \"leather bottle\" appearance and signet ring cells points to linitis plastica, which is a diffuse type of gastric carcinoma.","dimension":5,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.03714,0.069255,0.078672,0.086584,0.090415,0.092186,0.093118,0.090459,0.091096,0.089503,0.085315,0.096257],"unified_progress":[0.040414,0.053376,0.068784,0.081293,0.085982,0.092477,0.09257,0.094737,0.097155,0.095236,0.096555,0.10142]},{"section":18,"text":"Wait, but could it be something else?","dimension":12,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.029936,0.061809,0.07867,0.08721,0.093964,0.095184,0.097245,0.098388,0.098336,0.096237,0.088086,0.074934],"unified_progress":[0.038789,0.066825,0.080824,0.093499,0.095519,0.094196,0.097988,0.097542,0.095371,0.097518,0.08116,0.060769]},{"section":19,"text":"Let me think.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.29834,0.049702,0.050342,0.060146,0.061588,0.065132,0.063191,0.072084,0.075657,0.070974,0.075369,0.057476],"unified_progress":[0.20947,0.079819,0.065288,0.064642,0.074356,0.074612,0.092571,0.082622,0.079659,0.063728,0.059043,0.05419]},{"section":20,"text":"Gastric adenocarcinoma in general can present with weight loss, dyspepsia, and bleeding.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.039282,0.08375,0.059679,0.10005,0.10679,0.10404,0.10397,0.096069,0.087408,0.082469,0.073974,0.062513],"unified_progress":[0.0475,0.074244,0.062851,0.094603,0.1017,0.10068,0.10286,0.10063,0.095251,0.089303,0.074267,0.056104]},{"section":21,"text":"The \"leather bottle\" is more specific for linitis plastica, which is a poorly differentiated adenocarcinoma that infiltrates the stomach wall extensively, leading to the rigid stomach appearance.","dimension":5,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.034386,0.070807,0.081918,0.091946,0.097707,0.10073,0.10088,0.094518,0.094268,0.086448,0.074954,0.071439],"unified_progress":[0.039829,0.062726,0.082494,0.093666,0.099812,0.10376,0.10035,0.097305,0.095914,0.084479,0.074003,0.065666]},{"section":22,"text":"Unlike a polypoid or ulcerative type, this diffuse type spreads through the layers without forming a mass, hence the infiltration described.","dimension":5,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.032467,0.073815,0.086565,0.095426,0.097951,0.1008,0.10011,0.093863,0.096322,0.084476,0.072997,0.0652],"unified_progress":[0.034369,0.067594,0.087829,0.10008,0.10601,0.10709,0.10275,0.096866,0.095374,0.080928,0.066377,0.054737]},{"section":23,"text":"The signet ring cells are a big clue here.","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.035475,0.070814,0.084522,0.091653,0.094244,0.093512,0.094705,0.091833,0.090665,0.090157,0.082478,0.079942],"unified_progress":[0.042733,0.063181,0.078044,0.088743,0.09418,0.097496,0.097486,0.095705,0.093885,0.09096,0.083496,0.074092]},{"section":24,"text":"So the anemia could be due to chronic blood loss from the tumor, but in linitis plastica, the extensive infiltration might also cause bleeding.","dimension":9,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.028233,0.059964,0.072315,0.083119,0.092074,0.098258,0.1025,0.10005,0.098268,0.094283,0.089247,0.081683],"unified_progress":[0.036698,0.051154,0.064172,0.073149,0.084018,0.094642,0.096117,0.10061,0.10451,0.10489,0.10221,0.087832]},{"section":25,"text":"The pallor is from the anemia.","dimension":9,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.030922,0.06468,0.074127,0.081755,0.089558,0.095735,0.10024,0.10013,0.098334,0.094098,0.090398,0.080023],"unified_progress":[0.041016,0.05583,0.064323,0.07196,0.08283,0.091777,0.095479,0.099816,0.10375,0.10531,0.10193,0.085985]},{"section":26,"text":"No jaundice suggests that maybe the tumor isn't obstructing the biliary system yet, but it's possible that it's too early.","dimension":5,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.030224,0.067969,0.080007,0.087716,0.09204,0.097729,0.099696,0.09854,0.10154,0.091894,0.083856,0.068788],"unified_progress":[0.037712,0.06824,0.079873,0.088198,0.095239,0.097054,0.098545,0.097768,0.099019,0.094667,0.081862,0.061823]},{"section":27,"text":"Therefore, the most likely diagnosis is linitis plastica, which is a form of diffuse gastric carcinoma with signet ring cells and the characteristic radiographic finding.","dimension":7,"group":0,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.026559,0.053958,0.064085,0.073336,0.080679,0.086749,0.091627,0.09232,0.098217,0.095669,0.1003,0.1365],"unified_progress":[0.029423,0.043799,0.056727,0.067316,0.073398,0.083174,0.085369,0.091141,0.098166,0.0996,0.12169,0.1502]}]}}